OL,3,CInquest opens 34 years after woman
OL,4,Cvanished without trace
OL,6,FThe sister of a woman who went missing
OL,7,F34 years ago said the opening of an
OL,8,Finquest into her presumed death is a
OL,9,F"tremendous milestone".
OL,11,FMother-of-two Patricia Hall, from
OL,12,FPudsey, West Yorkshire, vanished in
OL,13,F1992 at the age of 39. Her body has
OL,14,Fnever been found.
OL,16,FMrs Hall's husband Keith was cleared
OL,17,Fof murder after a trial in 1994, after
OL,18,Fan alleged taped confession that he
OL,19,Fhad strangled her was ruled
OL,20,Finadmissible by a judge.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@VO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/11
