OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777558268
OL,3,CInquest opens 34 years after woman
OL,4,Cvanished without trace
OL,6,FAn inquest into Mrs Hall's death was
OL,7,Fopened and adjourned at Wakefield
OL,8,FCoroner's Court on Thursday by coroner
OL,9,FOliver Longstaff.
OL,11,FMr Longstaff said a fresh application
OL,12,Fto hold an inquest had been made to
OL,13,Fhim by Mrs Hall's sister, Christine
OL,14,FWeatherhead, and he had then
OL,15,Fsuccessfully applied for permission to
OL,16,Fthe deputy chief coroner, Judge
OL,17,FGeorgina Sharkey.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777558268
OL,3,CInquest opens 34 years after woman
OL,4,Cvanished without trace
OL,6,FThe coroner outlined how two courts
OL,7,Fhad made orders over the last 34 years
OL,8,Fpresuming Mrs Hall's death - a 2001
OL,9,Fruling granting Keith Hall a divorce
OL,10,Fand a 2006 High Court ruling granting
OL,11,Fprobate to her two sons.
OL,13,FMr Longstaff told the hearing that it
OL,14,Fwas "a very unusual set of
OL,15,Fcircumstances that has led us to be
OL,16,Fhere".
OL,18,FHe said that Mrs Hall was last seen on
OL,19,FJanuary 25 1992 "when family members
OL,20,Fspent the day in Ripon".
OL,26,@vD@EOUxD@EO]{D@QOU|D@WO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777558268
OL,3,CInquest opens 34 years after woman
OL,4,Cvanished without trace
OL,6,FThe coroner said there had been no
OL,7,Fsightings of her since, and no
OL,8,F"circumstantial evidence" she is
OL,9,Falive, including no attempts to use
OL,10,Fher bank accounts.
OL,12,FHe said Mrs Hall had not tried to
OL,13,F"contact any family member or social
OL,14,Facquaintances".
OL,16,FMr Longstaff said: "There is reason to
OL,17,Fsuspect that Mrs Hall's abrupt and
OL,18,Fcomplete disappearance is a
OL,19,Fconsequence of her having died a
OL,20,Fviolent or unnatural death."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@YO]uD@AOUvD@NO]xD@TOU|D@\O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777558268
OL,3,CInquest opens 34 years after woman
OL,4,Cvanished without trace
OL,6,FThe coroner said that Keith Hall had
OL,7,Fbeen contacted about Thursday's
OL,8,Fopening hearing but was "unable to
OL,9,Fmake arrangements to attend".
OL,11,FAdjourning the hearing to a date to be
OL,12,Ffixed, he said the court will be
OL,13,Finviting Mr Hall to provide a
OL,14,Fstatement.
OL,16,FSpeaking outside the court on
OL,17,FThursday, Mrs Weatherhead cried as she
OL,18,Fsaid: "We've tried so many times over
OL,19,Fthe last 34 years, it's quite a
OL,20,Ftremendous milestone.
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@\O]zD@GOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777558268
OL,3,CInquest opens 34 years after woman
OL,4,Cvanished without trace
OL,6,F"To finally get this day is hard to
OL,7,Fput into words."
OL,9,FShe said: "I've always said that she
OL,10,Fwould never have left her family `
OL,11,Fcertainly not her two boys.
OL,13,F"Something untoward has happened to
OL,14,FPat and hopefully this inquest will
OL,15,Fgive us that evidence about what may
OL,16,Fhave happened."
OL,18,FMrs Weatherhead said: "Pat was my big
OL,19,Fsister and she was just like a mother
OL,20,Fto all of us.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@PO]qD@KOUuD@AOUxD@OO]zD@WOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777558268
OL,3,CInquest opens 34 years after woman
OL,4,Cvanished without trace
OL,6,F"She was always there. She was always
OL,7,Fsupportive. She was always a buoyant,
OL,8,Fbright, bubbly person."
OL,10,FShe added: "I want that recognition
OL,11,Ffor Pat, in that she was a person, she
OL,12,Fwas a mum, she was a sister and a
OL,13,Fdaughter.
OL,15,F"I think after 34 years she deserves
OL,16,Fthat recognition. It's the least
OL,17,Feverybody can do for her."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@WO]rD@LOUwD@AOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777558268
OL,3,CInquest opens 34 years after woman
OL,4,Cvanished without trace
OL,6,FMrs Weatherhead added: "For 34 years,
OL,7,Fwe have fought the judicial system to
OL,8,Fhave Pat acknowledged not as missing,
OL,9,For just a number on a case file, but
OL,10,Fas a kind, loving, devoted mother,
OL,11,Fsister, and daughter who would never
OL,12,Fhave left her sons, Andrew and Graeme,
OL,13,For her family.
OL,15,F"Pat was known for her warmth and
OL,16,Fgenerosity, always putting her family
OL,17,Ffirst.
OL,19,F"Her absence has left a void that has
OL,20,Fnever been filled."
OL,26,@nD@XOUwD@AOU{D@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/11
