CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777558268
OL,3,CInquest opens 34 years after woman
OL,4,Cvanished without trace
OL,6,FKeith Hall was charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter he allegedly admitted on tape to
OL,8,Fan undercover policewoman, with whom
OL,9,Fhe had started a romance, that he had
OL,10,Fstrangled his wife and disposed of her
OL,11,Fbody in an incinerator.
OL,13,FAt his 1994 trial, the judge, Mr
OL,14,FJustice Waterhouse, ruled that the
OL,15,Ftape, which was obtained after Keith
OL,16,FHall answered a "lonely hearts"
OL,17,Fadvertisement in a local newspaper,
OL,18,Fwas inadmissible as evidence.
OL,26,@xD@QOUxD@_O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
