PN,36110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777558268
OL,3,CInquest opens 34 years after woman
OL,4,Cvanished without trace
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Sarah Jones,
OL,7,FWest Yorkshire Police lead for
OL,8,FSpecialist Crime and Criminal Justice,
OL,9,Fsaid on Thursday: "Our Major
OL,10,FInvestigation Review Team conducted a
OL,11,Fthorough cold case review into the
OL,12,Fdisappearance of Patricia Hall, which
OL,13,Fconcluded last year without uncovering
OL,14,Fany new lines of inquiries.
OL,16,F"Throughout the review, we remained in
OL,17,Fcontact with Patricia's family to
OL,18,Foffer support and keep them informed,
OL,19,Fand they were advised when the review
OL,20,Fcame to an end.
OL,26,@qD@SOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
