PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777558268
OL,3,CInquest opens 34 years after woman
OL,4,Cvanished without trace
OL,6,F"The case remains unsolved, and we
OL,7,Fcontinue to appeal for any new
OL,8,Finformation that may help provide
OL,9,FPatricia's family with the answers
OL,10,Fthey deserve."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
